name: Scrabble Cuff Links
description:
Item No. CUF001

Fun & Quirky Personalized Scrabble Cufflinks

Choose your letters from A - Z

Silver plated cufflinks.

All scrabble cufflinks are made to order so please alow 3 - 5 days for these to be made then dispatched. If you need them in an hurry just pop me a message and I will make them straight away and have them with you asap.

Excellent Gift for the Groom, grooms men, birthdays, new job, Father's Day etc

All cuff-links come in a black or silver cuff-links box, ready for that special person.

Please be advised, letters J, M, K,  are very popular letters and also harder to source. Due to this, there is a £1.00 extra charge when ordering letters J,M & K for cufflinks making these letters priced at £7.00 for a pair instead of £6.00. Please contact me if you have any questions.
